        <h2>Photography</h2>
        <p>I enjoy capturing moments and telling stories through the lens of my camera. Photography allows me to express my creativity and explore the beauty of the world around me. It enables me to connect with people, places, and emotions in a unique way, preserving memories that can be cherished for a lifetime. Through photography, I can experiment with light, composition, and perspective to create images that evoke feelings and tell powerful stories. Whether it's a breathtaking landscape, a candid moment, or a simple detail, photography gives me the opportunity to see the world with fresh eyes and share those moments with others..</p>
        <img src="https://example.com/photography-image.jpg" alt="Photography Hobby">
